title: #96 Mr. Mime
body:
Yeah babey!  We’re back in the REAL bootlegs.

The finger balls are less pronounced and there’s neither mouth nor rosy cheeks. This actually makes Mr. Mime LESS unsettling.

But then you also see that he’s just like.  Straddling a box and it’s very weird.

title: Kirby characters with Pokemon types
body:
A fun little thing I made. It’s kinda long. …it’s very long.

Kirby - Normal (certain copy abilities give him an extra type)
Meta Knight - Normal/Flying (Normal/Steel if he’s got his cape, just Normal if he doesn’t have his mask, and Steel/Flying if he has his robosuit)
Dedede - Ice/Flying
Bandana Dee - Fighting
Galacta Knight - Fairy/Steel
Marx - Fairy (Fairy/Dark when he makes his wish)
Magolor - Psychic (Ghost/Dark when he gets the crown)
Landia - Dragon
Taranza - Grass/Bug
Dark MK - Ghost/Flying
Daroach - Normal/Poison
Susie - Electric
Adeline - Normal
Ribbon - Fairy
Rick - Fire/Rock
Kine - Water
Coo - Flying
Hyness - Poison/Psychic
Whispy Woods - Grass
Morpho Knight - Bug/Fire
Prince Fluff - Normal
Gooey - Water/Rock

I might edit this later and add more characters.

It’s been just over four years since I’ve created Rainie, so I thought it was about time to give her a nicer, updated ref! Not
...
caption:
It’s been just over four years since I’ve created Rainie, so I thought it was about time to give her a nicer, updated ref! Not too much has changed other than a bow on her black sash, socks peeking out of her boots, a bow on her headband and a heart scale necklace!
Oh, and her hair got fluffier?
